To play 2 player game:
  Decide who is hosting and who will join the game
  
  HOST:
   + Run "python2.6 network.py host" on a compatible (student) machine
   + Wait for the other player to join
   
  JOINING (Client):
   + Get the hostname for the client (preferably IP)
   + Run "python2.6 network.py join <HOST IP>
  
  Game will Launch
  
  To Play the Game:
    * use WASD to move your ship (blue)
    * Fire your laser with left click at the enemy (gold)
    * Winner is last man standing (and can revel in their glory for all eternity)
    * Be careful of your own fire
    
  
